phase "Welcome" "This is the **Runner view**: a clean form where you set inputs and hit Run.\n\nThe **Builder view** (toggle in the top-right) shows the full canvas with nodes and wires. This project adds two numbers together using a Code node and displays the result below.\n\nChange the numbers, hit Run, and watch the output update." {
  field number_1 value label:"First Number" description:"Feeds into the Code node. Try any number."
  field number_2 value label:"Second Number" description:"The Code node adds this to the first number."
}

output debug data label:"Result" description:"The sum of your two numbers, plus a greeting message."
